1
00:00:00,249 --> 00:00:04,059
I try to envision the events that take
place as individual elements.

2
00:00:04,280 --> 00:00:08,540
I can then make a note of each one,
but I gain a better understanding when I

3
00:00:08,541 --> 00:00:14,020
combine all of these again as a whole,
which is why I have very bad handwriting.

4
00:00:16,580 --> 00:00:17,620
Any other questions?

5
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:18,920
Oh, oh!

6
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:21,117
Can you tell me if there's
something that you're not

7
00:00:21,118 --> 00:00:23,420
good at, or maybe something
that you're scared of?

8
00:00:23,740 --> 00:00:25,300
Something I'm scared of?

9
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:25,940
What?

10
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:27,160
Yeah, right.

11
00:00:27,220 --> 00:00:28,480
Elle's not scared of anything.

12
00:00:28,481 --> 00:00:29,900
Well, I suppose.

13
00:00:30,100 --> 00:00:31,100
Monsters.

14
00:00:31,400 --> 00:00:32,400
Me too.

15
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:33,640
I am too.

16
00:00:33,879 --> 00:00:35,780
Dummy, Elle's not the same as you.

17
00:00:36,449 --> 00:00:39,760
There are many types of monsters in this
world.

18
00:00:40,534 --> 00:00:43,220
Monsters who will not show themselves and
who cause trouble.

19
00:00:43,625 --> 00:00:45,320
Monsters who abduct children.

20
00:00:45,495 --> 00:00:47,800
Monsters who devour dreams.

21
00:00:48,260 --> 00:00:49,400
Monsters who suck blood.

22
00:00:50,224 --> 00:00:53,640
And monsters who always tell lies.

23
00:00:54,400 --> 00:00:56,840
Lying monsters are a real nuisance.

24
00:00:56,841 --> 00:00:59,300
They are much more cunning than other
monsters.

25
00:00:59,301 --> 00:01:00,301
A little pause...

